'''Bonadan Heavy Industries''', also know as '''Bonadan Industries''', was a subsidiary company of [[Tagge Company/Legends|TaggeCo]].<ref name="HSCS" /> The company produced the [[Cargo-Mover Tractor Beam]].<ref name="PP" /> During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], [[Eanis Malavoy]] was employed as a buyer for Bonadan Heavy Industries.<ref name="HAT">''[[Honor Among Thieves]]''</ref>

